thread.title: TV | Doctor Who

author: Fiona Flynn
title: TV | Doctor Who
text: Game of Thrones fans will see a familiar face in tonight's Doctor Who as Maisie Williams, (who plays Arya Stark in the hit show), makes her much anticipated appearance in what will be the first of two parts. She plays a Viking girl that the Doctor and Clara meet when they are captured by Vikings and must help protect their village from attack by space warriors from the future known as the Mire. As you do.
